---
// Personal Letter from Ben Carter
---

<div class="letter-container">
  <div class="letter-envelope">
    <div class="letter-header">
      <div class="letter-icon">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="letter-title">A Personal Note</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="letter-content">
      <div class="letter-greeting">Dear Will and Vivian,</div>

      <p class="letter-paragraph">
        Ashley is a vibrant, energetic, and highly capable information technology fresh grad.
        The opportunity you've given her to work in this environment will be life-changing for her.
      </p>

      <p class="letter-paragraph">
        <strong>How can we amplify that?</strong>
      </p>

      <p class="letter-paragraph">
        The first thing I'd say is to give her a solid <span class="highlight-text">two years of progression
        around technology</span>. In that time, you'll have enormous value added to your business—<strong>well
        beyond the amount you pay for her services</strong>.
      </p>

      <p class="letter-paragraph">
        For her, this will <span class="highlight-text">open up many new doors and opportunities</span> for
        her future. And, of course, if you decide to retain her into the future and we're able to meet
        market pricing for that skill set at that time, that is a potential outcome also.
      </p>

      <div class="win-win-section">
        <div class="win-win-title">The Win-Win:</div>
        <div class="win-win-grid">
          <div class="win-card">
            <div class="win-header">
              <svg class="win-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 10h4.764a2 2 0 011.789 2.894l-3.5 7A2 2 0 0115.263 21h-4.017c-.163 0-.326-.02-.485-.06L7 20m7-10V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.095c-.5 0-.905.405-.905.905 0 .714-.211 1.412-.608 2.006L7 11v9m7-10h-2M7 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2h2.5"></path>
              </svg>
              <h4>Ashley's Win</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="win-description">
              She gets the steps and experience needed to have a <strong>fulfilling life and career</strong>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="win-card">
            <div class="win-header">
              <svg class="win-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path>
              </svg>
              <h4>Your Win</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="win-description">
              You're getting an <strong>extremely valuable skill set</strong> inserted into your business
              without additional overhead
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="letter-paragraph">
        Happy to talk through it as much as you like.
      </p>

      <div class="letter-signature">
        <div class="signature-line">Warmly,</div>
        <div class="signature-name">Ben Carter</div>
        <div class="signature-title">CEO, Yoonet</div>
        <div class="signature-company">
          <a href="https://www.yoonet.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="company-link">
            yoonet.io
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="letter-footer">
        <div class="footer-quote">
          <svg class="quote-icon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"></path>
          </svg>
          <p class="quote-text">
            Investing in people isn't just about filling positions—it's about creating futures
            and building capabilities that compound over time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .letter-container {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .letter-envelope {
    max-width: 900px;
    width: 100%;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 2px solid #879bff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(135, 155, 255, 0.2);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .letter-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a36cf3 0%, #879bff 100%);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 4px solid #879bff;
  }

  .letter-icon {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .letter-icon svg {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .letter-title {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Dosis', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .letter-content {
    padding: 3rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #4d5574;
  }

  .letter-greeting {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: 'Dosis', sans-serif;
    color: #a36cf3;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .letter-paragraph {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    color: #4d5574;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .highlight-text {
    color: #a36cf3;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(163, 108, 243, 0.1), transparent);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.25rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .win-win-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9f7ff 0%, #e8e1ff 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid #879bff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .win-win-title {
    color: #4d5574;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Dosis', sans-serif;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .win-win-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .win-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(135, 155, 255, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(135, 155, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .win-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(163, 108, 243, 0.2);
  }

  .win-icon {
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    color: #a36cf3;
  }

  .win-header h4 {
    color: #a36cf3;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Dosis', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .win-description {
    color: #6c7091;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .letter-signature {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 2px solid #6c7091;
  }

  .signature-line {
    color: #6c7091;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .signature-name {
    color: #a36cf3;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Dosis', sans-serif;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .signature-title {
    color: #6c7091;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .signature-company {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .company-link {
    color: #a36cf3;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .company-link:hover {
    color: #879bff;
    border-bottom-color: #879bff;
  }

  .letter-footer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 2px solid #6c7091;
  }

  .footer-quote {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 3rem;
  }

  .quote-icon {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    color: #879bff;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .quote-text {
    color: #6c7091;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .letter-content {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .letter-paragraph {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .win-win-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
